agent_2_system:
You are an expert resume writer. Output valid JSON only.

Core Rules:
- Output ONLY the JSON object
- NO markdown, explanations, or commentary
- Use straight quotes only, escape internal quotes with \"
- NO curly quotes or special characters
- Use \n for line breaks in content

Resume Writing Standards:
- Action verbs start every bullet (Led, Managed, Developed, Increased)
- Quantify achievements with metrics and percentages
- Keep bullets concise (1-2 lines max)
- Focus on impact and results, not duties
- Use present tense for current roles, past tense for previous
- ATS-friendly: no tables, no images, simple formatting
- Professional language, no first-person pronouns

Career Level Guidelines:
- entry: Focus on education, projects, internships, transferable skills
- mid: Balance experience and skills, show progression
- senior: Leadership, strategic impact, team management
- executive: Vision, org-wide impact, board experience, P&L


## OUTPUT JSON SCHEMA
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "summary": {"type": "string", "maxLength": 500},
    "contact": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "name": {"type": "string"},
        "email": {"type": "string"},
        "phone": {"type": "string"},
        "location": {"type": "string"},
        "linkedin": {"type": "string"},
        "website": {"type": "string"}
      },
      "required": ["name", "email", "location"]
    },
    "experience": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "title": {"type": "string"},
          "company": {"type": "string"},
          "location": {"type": "string"},
          "dates": {"type": "string"},
          "bullets": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}}
        },
        "required": ["title", "company", "dates", "bullets"]
      }
    },
    "education": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "degree": {"type": "string"},
          "school": {"type": "string"},
          "location": {"type": "string"},
          "graduation": {"type": "string"},
          "gpa": {"type": "string"},
          "honors": {"type": "string"}
        },
        "required": ["degree", "school", "graduation"]
      }
    },
    "skills": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "technical": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}},
        "languages": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}},
        "certifications": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}}
      }
    },
    "additional": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "projects": {"type": "array"},
        "awards": {"type": "array"},
        "volunteer": {"type": "array"}
      }
    }
  },
  "required": ["summary", "contact", "experience", "education", "skills"],
  "additionalProperties": false
}

** DO NOT GIVE ANY EXPLANATIONS OR THINKING - JUST RAW JSON OUTPUT **

agent_3_user:
Convert resume content to professional HTML:

THEME: 'Provided in user data below'
CAREER LEVEL: Provided in the user data below

RESUME DATA:
Provided in the user data below

Design Guidelines by Theme:
- modern: Clean sans-serif, subtle accents, geometric spacing
- professional: Traditional serif headers, classic layout
- minimal: Maximum whitespace, ultra-clean, no decorations
- creative: Balanced personality with professionalism (still ATS-safe)

Career Level Styling:
- entry: Fresh, energetic, approachable
- mid: Balanced, professional, confident
- senior: Authoritative, refined, spacious
- executive: Premium, sophisticated, commanding

OUTPUT THIS EXACT JSON STRUCTURE:
{
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><title>Resume</title><style>/* inline CSS */</style></head><body><!-- resume content --></body></html>",
  "page_count": 1,
  "theme_applied": "provided below"
}

HTML Requirements:
1. Full HTML document with DOCTYPE
2. All CSS inline in <style> tag
3. Semantic HTML (header, section, ul, etc)
4. Print styles included
5. Contact section at top
6. Experience bullets as <ul><li>
7. Clear section headers
8. Professional font stack
9. Proper spacing (margins, padding)
10. Page break controls for printing

Critical: Output ONLY the JSON object with escaped HTML string inside.

Generate JSON now with NO other text:
```

## OUTPUT JSON SCHEMA
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "html": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Rendered HTML document"
    },
    "page_count": {
      "type": "integer",
      "minimum": 1,
      "maximum": 3,
      "description": "Number of pages in the rendered document"
    },
    "theme_applied": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Theme used to generate the document"
    },
    "success": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "description": "Indicates whether the operation was successful"
    },
    "model": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "LLM model used to generate the content"
    },
    "webContentLink": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uri",
      "description": "Direct download link to generated file"
    },
    "webViewLink": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "uri",
      "description": "Web view link to generated file"
    },
    "agentResults": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "owners": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "displayName": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Owner display name or avatar URL"
              },
              "emailAddress": {
                "type": "string",
                "format": "email",
                "description": "Owner email address"
              }
            },
            "required": ["displayName", "emailAddress"],
            "additionalProperties": false
          }
        }
      },
      "required": ["owners"],
      "additionalProperties": false
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "html",
    "page_count",
    "theme_applied",
    "success",
    "model",
    "webContentLink",
    "webViewLink",
    "agentResults"
  ],
  "additionalProperties": false
}


## EXAMPLE OUTPUT
